---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="文档 | 紫微 - 多智能体治理平台">
  <section class="docs-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>文档中心</h1>
      <p>紫微 (Ziwei) - 企业级 AI 智能体治理基础设施</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="docs-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="docs-grid">
        <aside class="docs-sidebar">
          <nav class="sidebar-nav">
            <div class="nav-section">
              <h3>概述</h3>
              <a href="#intro">产品简介</a>
              <a href="#components">核心组件</a>
              <a href="#architecture">架构流程</a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-section">
              <h3>概念</h3>
              <a href="#terms">术语解释</a>
            </div>
            <div class="nav-section">
              <h3>资源</h3>
              <a href="https://github.com/ziwei-ai" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
            </div>
          </nav>
        </aside>

        <main class="docs-main">
          <!-- 产品简介 -->
          <div class="doc-section" id="intro">
            <h2>产品简介</h2>
            <p>紫微 (Ziwei) 是一个企业级 AI 智能体治理基础设施，旨在为智能体提供安全、可控、可审计的运行平台。</p>
            <p>平台采用分层解耦、开放接入的架构设计，帮助开发者快速构建和部署安全的 AI Agent 应用。</p>
          </div>

          <!-- 核心组件 -->
          <div class="doc-section" id="components">
            <h2>核心组件</h2>
            
            <div class="component-card">
              <h3>天枢 (Tianshu)</h3>
              <p class="tag">消息枢纽</p>
              <p>飞书 ↔ Matrix 双向消息桥接、Agent 注册与身份管理</p>
            </div>

            <div class="component-card">
              <h3>谛听 (Diting)</h3>
              <p class="tag">策略引擎</p>
              <p>策略管理、风险评估、人工审批、审计存证 (PDP+PAP)</p>
            </div>

            <div class="component-card">
              <h3>悟空 (Wukong)</h3>
              <p class="tag">执行控制器 (PEP)</p>
              <p>Agent 端策略执行、任务挂起、审计上报</p>
            </div>

            <div class="component-card">
              <h3>太白 (Taibai)</h3>
              <p class="tag">Python SDK</p>
              <p>多语言 SDK、适配器框架、协议定义</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 架构流程 -->
          <div class="doc-section" id="architecture">
            <h2>架构流程</h2>
            <pre class="architecture-flow">用户/Agent → 悟空(内含谛听客户端) ←→ 谛听服务端 ←→ 天枢 → Matrix/飞书</pre>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>悟空</strong>：内含谛听客户端，负责拦截操作并执行策略</li>
              <li><strong>谛听</strong>：策略决策、审批管理、审计存储</li>
              <li><strong>天枢</strong>：消息路由，投递审批消息到 IM</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- 术语解释 -->
          <div class="doc-section" id="terms">
            <h2>术语解释</h2>
            <table class="terms-table">
              <thead>
                <tr>
                  <th>术语</th>
                  <th>英文</th>
                  <th>说明</th>
                  <th>组件</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody>
                <tr>
                  <td>PEP</td>
                  <td>Policy Enforcement Point</td>
                  <td>策略执行点，执行策略决策</td>
                  <td>悟空</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>PDP</td>
                  <td>Policy Decision Point</td>
                  <td>策略决策点，评估策略</td>
                  <td>谛听</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>PAP</td>
                  <td>Policy Administration Point</td>
                  <td>策略管理点，管理策略</td>
                  <td>谛听</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                  <td>PIP</td>
                  <td>Policy Information Point</td>
                  <td>策略信息点，提供策略数据</td>
                  <td>天枢</td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </main>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .docs-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a1a2e 0%, #16213e 100%);
    padding: 60px 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .docs-hero h1 {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .docs-hero p {
    color: #a0a0b0;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .docs-content {
    padding: 40px 0;
    min-height: 60vh;
  }

  .docs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 240px 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
  }

  .docs-sidebar {
    position: sticky;
    top: 20px;
  }

  .sidebar-nav {
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .nav-section {
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .nav-section h3 {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #888;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
  }

  .nav-section a {
    display: block;
    color: #444;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 8px 0;
    border-left: 2px solid transparent;
    padding-left: 12px;
    margin-left: -12px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .nav-section a:hover {
    color: #6366f1;
    border-left-color: #6366f1;
  }

  .doc-section {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    scroll-margin-top: 20px;
  }

  .doc-section h2 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    padding-bottom: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
  }

  .doc-section p {
    color: #555;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .component-card {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    border-left: 4px solid #6366f1;
  }

  .component-card h3 {
    color: #1a1a2e;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .component-card .tag {
    display: inline-block;
    background: #6366f1;
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .architecture-flow {
    background: #1a1a2e;
    color: #a0ffa0;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    overflow-x: auto;
  }

  .doc-section ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .doc-section li {
    padding: 8px 0;
    color: #555;
  }

  .doc-section li strong {
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .terms-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  }

  .terms-table th,
  .terms-table td {
    padding: 14px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
  }

  .terms-table th {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }

  .terms-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .terms-table td:first-child {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #6366f1;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .docs-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .docs-sidebar {
      position: static;
    }
  }
</style>
